<header>
	Listen to Part One of an interview with Zenia. Are the following statements true or false?
</header>
	
<section id="body">
	<video class="rightFloat" src="../Media/Unit01_e3.flv" mode="1" id="1003"  /><br/><ol id="questionList"><br/><li id="1">The Examiner introduces herself to the candidate.<a id="q1" >True</a><tab/><a id="q2" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="2">Zenia has to give the Examiner her full name.<a id="q3" >True</a><tab/><a id="q4" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="3">Zenia does not need to produce identification.<a id="q5" >True</a><tab/><a id="q6" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="4">The candidate has a turn to ask questions.<a id="q7" >True</a><tab/><a id="q8" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="5">The candidate is asked where she comes from.<a id="q9" >True</a><tab/><a id="q10" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="6">The candidate asks the Examiner her name.<a id="q11" >True</a><tab/><a id="q12" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="7">Zenia is asked to describe her home town.<a id="q13" >True</a><tab/><a id="q14" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="8">The Examiner asks Zenia about her family.<a id="q15" >True</a><tab/><a id="q16" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="9">The candidate is asked where she was born.<a id="q17" >True</a><tab/><a id="q18" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="10">The Examiner asks Zenia to talk about her life.<a id="q19" >True</a><tab/><a id="q20" >False</a><br/></li></ol>
